<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Forgot Password | FaceAI Attend</title>
  <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/7.0.1/css/all.min.css" crossorigin="anonymous" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" />
</head>
<body>
  <main class="auth-shell dual-auth-shell">
    <section class="auth-panel reveal">
      <span class="status-chip"><span class="live-dot"></span> Admin recovery</span>
      <h1>Admin OTP Reset</h1>
      <p>Admin password reset uses email OTP. After an SMTP or OTP provider is connected, this form will send the reset code.</p>
      <form class="stack-form auth-form">
        <label><span>Admin Email</span><input type="email" placeholder="admin@company.com"></label>
        <button class="btn btn-primary wide" type="button"><i class="fa-solid fa-envelope-circle-check"></i> Send OTP</button>
      </form>
      <p class="form-status">Recovery policy: email OTP reset system for admins.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="auth-panel reveal">
      <span class="status-chip"><span class="live-dot"></span> Employee recovery</span>
      <h1>Employee Recovery</h1>
      <p>Employees do not sign in with passwords. Recovery is handled through admin reset or face verification plus OTP.</p>
      <div class="permission-list">
        <span><i class="fa-solid fa-user-shield"></i> Admin reset only</span>
        <span><i class="fa-solid fa-fingerprint"></i> Face verification + OTP</span>
      </div>
      <a href="/login" class="btn btn-secondary wide"><i class="fa-solid fa-fingerprint"></i> Back to Face Login</a>
    </section>
  </main>
</body>
</html>
